dmca.title: Individual complains of blogged photos
dmca.body:

Additionally they have been accessed by an act of theft and posted on Blogspot.

3)	My contact details are [private]@bessiebardot.com TEL [private] MOB [private]

4)	I have good faith belief that use of the copyrighted material described above on the allefedly infringing web pages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.

5)	I swear under penalty of perjury that the information in the notification is accurate and that I am the copyright owner.

Bessie Bardot
